-   <span data-ttu-id="6d539-117">Значение свойства <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> — `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d539-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="6d539-118">Уровень достоверности искусственный семантической 1.0 (возвращенный <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d539-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
